desc.desc: Moves 5th argument one position to the left.

example.desc:
{{- powerjinja.arguments.move_fifth_left(arg1, arg2, arg3, arg4, arg5, macros=[powerjinja.core.print]) -}}
// prints arg1 arg2 arg3 arg5 arg5

desc.desc: Moves 5th argument one position to the right.

example.desc:
{{- powerjinja.arguments.move_fifth_right(arg1, arg2, arg3, arg4, arg5, macros=[powerjinja.core.print]) -}}
// prints arg5 arg2 arg3 arg4 arg5

desc.desc: Moves 1st argument one position to the left.

example.desc:

example.desc:

desc.desc: Reverses argument order.

example.desc:
{{- powerjinja.arguments.reverse(arg1, arg2, arg3, arg4, arg5, macros=[powerjinja.core.print]) -}}
// prints arg5 arg4 arg3 arg2 arg1

desc.desc: Shifts all arguments one position to the left.

example.desc:
{{- powerjinja.arguments.shift_left(arg1, arg2, arg3, arg4, arg5, macros=[powerjinja.core.print]) -}}
// prints arg2 arg3 arg4 arg5 arg1

desc.desc: Shifts all arguments one position to the right.

example.desc:
{{- powerjinja.arguments.shift_right(arg1, arg2, arg3, arg4, arg5, macros=[powerjinja.core.print]) -}}
// prints arg5 arg1 arg2 arg3 arg4
